Squizzy::

She swallowed hard and tried to relax alittle.  But is made her 
nervous that he would darken the windows.  She wondered if was done 
so she could see where they were going.  She tried to lean back and 
relax, but the arrow hit the seat and made her wince in pain.  She 
swallowed hard and tried to make her voice sound calm,"Would you at 
least tell me your name?"  She paused,  "Please?"


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Dark One::
> 
> "I'm afraid I can't let you out," says Dark One, still over his 
intercom, 
> "You won't make it very far on your own anyhow."
> 
> He pauses for a while, leaving most of her questions unanswered as 
the window 
> she had been looking out of darkened and finally went completely 
black. "Rest 
> for now. We'll arrive shortly."
